</div></li><li> Corey Hart's <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SunglassesAtNight" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SunglassesAtNight">Sunglasses at Night</a></em> is about life in one of these, mixed with <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/StalkerWithACrush" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/StalkerWithACrush">Stalker with a Crush</a>.
